 <name>Auth_SASL</name>
 <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
 <summary>Abstraction of various SASL mechanism responses</summary>
 <description>
Provides code to generate responses to common SASL mechanisms, including:
- Digest-MD5
- CramMD5
- Plain
- Anonymous
- Login (Pseudo mechanism)
 </description>

